quran[38]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"Neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã la b gɩdg nebã n yi Wẽnd sorã, A sãama bãmb tʋʋma."
  47,2,"La neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩd la b tʋm sõma, la b kõ sɩd ne bũmb ning sẽn sik a Mohammad zugã - yẽ me la sɩda n yi bãmb Soabã nengẽ - A yẽesa bãmb rãmb yel-beed n yi-ba, la A maneg b yεla."
  47,3,"Yaa woto bala, tɩ neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã, b pʋga zĩri, la neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩdã, b pʋga sɩd sẽn yi b Soabã nengẽ; yaa woto bal la Wẽnd wilgd nebã, b tɑɑbã bilg-n-taare."
  47,4,"Yãmb sã n wa yek neb nins sẽn kɩfl-ba (zabrẽ), yaa yubli keeb bala, hal tɩ yãmb sã n wa koms-ba, bɩ y keng sẽbrã ma tɩ y bas taale, ma tɩ y reeg yõor yaoodo, hal tɩ zabrã wa tɩ rɩgl a zɩɩbo. Yaa woto bala, la Wẽnd sã n rag n tʋlla, A naan n halk-ba, la yaa sẽn na yɩl n zarb yãmb ne taab n gese. Neb nins b sẽn kʋ Wẽnd Sorã zugã, A kõn yeeb b tʋʋm lae-lae ye."
  47,5,"A na n peeg-b lame la A maneg b yεla."
  47,6,"La A kẽes-b Arzãna, A sẽn rag n sɩf-bɑ wilg-b dĩni wã."
  47,7,"Yãmb ɑ neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnde! Y sã n sõng Wẽnde, A sõngd-y lame, la A tabl y nao-kadma."
  47,8,"La neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã, yaalg be ne-ba, la A sãɑm b tʋʋmã."
  47,9,"Yaa woto bala, tɩ ad bãmb kisga Wẽnd sẽn sik bũmb ningã t'A lub bãmb tʋʋmã."
  47,10,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmb pa kẽnd Tẽngã zug n get wãn-wãn la neb nins sẽn reng bãmb taoorã baasg yɩ yã? Wẽnd pama b zugu, rẽnda buud n be ne kɩfr-dãmba."
  47,11,"Yaa woto bala, tɩ yaa Wẽnd la neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã lall-n-taaga, la neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã, bãmb pa tar lalld ye."
  47,12,"Wẽnd kẽesda neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã la b tʋm sõama wã Arzãn-rãmbẽ, ko-sood sẽn zoet b tẽngre, la neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã wʋmda noog la b rɩtẽ wala rũmsã sẽn rɩtã, la Bugmã la bãmb gãag zĩiga."
  47,13,"La sõor waoog tẽng sẽn yɩɩd fo tẽng ning sẽn yiis-foo wã ne keelem, lɑ Tõnd yaool n halk-b lɑme, tɩ sõngd pa be ne-b ye."
  47,14,"Rẽ yĩnga, ned ning sẽn be vẽenem zugu, sẽn yi a Soabã nengẽ, wõndɑ wala ned ning b sẽn faas a tʋʋm-wẽng t'ɑ ne-ɑ t'ɑ yɑɑ neere, la b tũ b yõe yamleoodo?."
  47,15,"Arzãn ning b sẽn pʋlem ne Wẽnd zoεtbã bilgri: ko-sood n be a pʋgẽ sẽn yaa koom sẽn pa tedgde, la ko-sor sẽn yaa bĩisim, a noosmã pa tedgd ye; la ko-sood sẽn yaa noosem yũudbã yĩnga, la ko-sood sẽn yaa sɩɩd sẽn yɩlge. La b leb n tar a pʋgẽ tɩ-biisã fãa gilli, la yaafa sẽn yi b Soabã nengẽ. Rẽ yĩnga, wã na yɩ wala neb nins sẽn duumd Bugmã pʋgẽ tɩ b yũnug-b ko-tʋʋlg t'a fãs b yãadã?"
  47,16,"La be b (kɩfr-dãmbã) pʋgẽ, ned ning sẽn kelgd foom hal tɩ b sã n wa yi fo nengẽ la b sẽn yet neb nins b sẽn kõ bãngrã: ""yaa bõe la a sẽn da yet moas-moasã wã? "" Bãmb la neb nins Wẽnd sẽn pag b sũyã tɩ b pʋgd b yamleoodo."
  47,17,"La neb nins sẽn kãndgã, A paasa bãmb kãndgr la A kõ-b b wẽn-zoεεgã."
  47,18,"La rẽ yĩnga, bãmbã rãmbã gũuda bũmb tɩ sã n pa rũni wã yikr sẽn na n wa b nengẽ ne lingri. La sɩd la hakɩɩka, a tagmas-rãmbã zoe n waame. La bãmbã na n yɩɩ wãn n tẽeg t'a sã n wa wa bãmb (ne lingri)?"
  47,19,"Bɩ f bãng ne hakɩɩk tɩ soab kae tɩ sã n pa Wẽnd ye. La f kos yaafa f zunuubã yĩnga, la muumin roapã la muumin pogsã me zunuub yĩnga. Lɑ Wẽnd mii yãmb lεbeng zĩiga, la yãmb gãag zĩiga."
  47,20,"La neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã yetame: ""b pa na n sik Sʋʋra?"" Tɩ b sã n yaool n sik sʋʋra sẽn bʋ n manege, n tẽeg zabr a pʋgẽ fo yãta neb nins bãag sẽn be b rãmb sũyẽ wã tɩ b get foo wala ned sẽn sobg kũum yĩng gesgo, lɑ sẽn sõmba ne-ba."
  47,21,"Tũudum la gomd sẽn be neere. La yellã sã n wa loe n wãag bɩ f bãng tɩ bãmb sã n da kõẽ Wẽnd sɩda na yɩẽ sõma ne-ba."
  47,22,"La rẽ yĩnga y pa yaeesd tɩ y sã n gũd kuidga, yaa sãang bal la y na n sãeeg tẽngã zug la y wãag rogem, wɑlɑ y sã n dɑ mɑɑn zɩɩlemã sɑsɑ wã?"
  47,23,"Sẽn mɑɑnd-b rẽ wã bãmb rãmbɑ lɑ Wẽnd sẽn kãab-ba, n wʋng-ba tɩ b kɑ wʋmd sɩd ye, la A zong b ninã."
  47,24,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmb pa tagsd Alkʋrãanã n getẽ-la, bɩ yaa kʋɩlem-biisi n be b sũyẽ wã?"
  47,25,"Ad neb nins sẽn tar n lebg poorẽ kãndgrã sẽn vẽneg ne bãmb poorã , yaa a Sʋɩtãan n liib-ba la a walem-ba."
  47,26,"Yaa woto tɩ bãmb yeela neb nins sẽn kisg bũmb ning Wẽnd sẽn sikã: ""d na n tũ-y-la yel-sãnda pʋgẽ"". La Wẽnd mii b solgrã."
  47,27,"La na n yɩ wãn-wãn tɩ Malεgsã sã n wa kʋʋd bãmba, n pãbd bãmb nensã, la b poayã?"
  47,28,"Yɩta boto bal tɩ bala bãmb tũu bũmb ning sẽn gẽed Wẽndã, la b kisg A yardã t'A lub bãmb tʋʋmã."
  47,29,"Bɩ neb nins bãag sẽn be b rãmb sũyẽ wã tẽedame tɩ Wẽnd pa na n tol n mɑɑn tɩ bãmb beemɑ lɑ b kisgrã yi n vẽneg tɩ nebɑ bãng-bɑ."
  47,30,"La Tõnd sã n da tʋlla, M naan n wilg-f-ba. La fo na bãng-b ne b tagmas-rãmbã, fo na bãng-b neer-neer b gom bɩndmã pʋgẽ. La Wẽnd mii yãmb tʋʋmã."
  47,31,"La Tõnd na zarb yãmb neer-neere, hal n wa bãng nidg pãng rãmb Wẽnd Sorã zugu, la sugr rãmba, la D zɑrb yãmb n ges n mɑɑn tɩ b bãng yãmb sɩd-soɑbɑ lɑ y zĩri-be-nedɑ."
  47,32,"Ad neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã la b gɩd Wẽnd Sorã la b maan tẽn-tʋʋmã beem kãndgrã sẽn vẽneg ne bãmb poorẽ, b kõn tol n nams Wẽnd ba fʋɩ, A na n luba b tʋʋmã me."
  47,33,"Yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnde! Tũ-y Wẽnde, la y tũ Tẽn-tʋʋmã la y ra sãam y tʋʋm ye."
  47,34,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, neb nins sẽn kɩfl-b la b gɩd Wẽnd Sorã, rẽ poorẽ tɩ b ki tɩ b kell n ya kɩfr-dãmbã, Wẽnd kõn tol n yaaf-b ye."
  47,35,"Bɩ y ra valems ye, la y ra baood laafɩ rabeem yĩng ye, tɩ yãmb n yaool n be zugẽ. Wẽnd bee ne yãmba, A kõn tol n boog yãmb tʋʋmã me."
  47,36,"Ad Dũni wã vɩɩmã yaa wɩsg la reem. La yãmb sã n kõ sɩd la y zoe Wẽnde, A kõta yãmb y keoorã, la A pa modgd yãmb y arzεkẽ wã ye."
  47,37,"A sã n modgd yãmb a pʋgẽ n pẽdg yãmba, y maanda beed la A yiis yãmb kisgrã."
  47,38,"Ad yãmba, b boonda yãmb tɩ y yãk n naf Wẽnd Sorã zugu. La bee yãmb pʋgẽ sẽn maand beedo. La ned ning sẽn maand-a beedo, ad a maand a meng beedo. Wẽnd yaa Sek-m-meng Soaba, yãmb la tʋlsdba. Y sã n gõd y kuidga, A tedgda yãmb ne zẽms sẽn pa yãmba, rẽ poorẽ b pa yɩt wala yãmb buud ye."
